We absolutely love the @alucab_usa canopy camper. My advice to anyone looking into getting a canopy camper is fill out build sheet through @tinyrigco and build it according to your budget and needs.

For starters, 4 items I recommend when ordering are the 13gl water tank, @alucab_usa table slide,@gp_factor folding table and the @alucab_usa 270 shadow awning. These 4 products I use ALL the time.

For those that want to go all out, there are many options like the @dickinsonmarine furnace, @goosegear Utility cabinets, Screen Kits, Solar packages and more. 

Give @tinyrigco a call or head over to their HQ in Westminster CA, I’m sure they’ll gladly walk you through the whole entire process. Tell them I said hi 🙌🏻

To be honest with you guys, I’m not the biggest fan of roof top tents. This is why I chose to go with the @goosegear ultimate chef and sleep package. This allows me to crawl into bed, have a place to cook a meal and keep everything organized. The @hestoutdoors foamy mattress and the sleeping bag were also a must. It’s the most comfortable camping mattress ever, what a perfect combo. 

Yes the tent is for sale! 
Message me if you’re interested.
